{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"13523","heading":"Management plan","label":"13523 Management plan","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch134/schXI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Plan preparation","label":"a Plan preparation","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary, in consultation with the Advisory Board established under , shall prepare a management plan for the conduct of research, development, demonstration, and commercial application of energy technologies that is consistent with the goals stated in .section 13522 of this titlesection 13401 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Contents of plan","label":"b Contents of plan","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"investigation of promising energy and energy efficiency resource technologies that have been identified as potentially significant future contributors to national energy security;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"development of energy and energy efficiency resource technologies that have the potential to reduce energy supply vulnerability, and to minimize adverse impacts on the environment, the global climate, and the economy; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"creation of opportunities for export of energy and energy efficiency resource technologies from the United States that can enhance the Nation’s competitiveness.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Energy technology inventory and status report","label":"c Energy technology inventory and status report","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fc%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"degree of technological maturity; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fc%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the barriers posed by capital, operating, and maintenance costs;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"technical performance; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1/B/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fc%2F1%2FB%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"potential environmental impacts;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the projected time frame for commercial availability, specifying at a minimum whether the technology will be commercially available in the near-term, mid-term, or long-term, whether there are too many uncertainties to project availability, or whether it is unlikely that the technology will ever be commercial; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a projection of the future cost-competitiveness of the technology in comparison with alternative technologies to provide the same energy service.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Public comment","label":"d Public comment","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall publish the proposed management plan for a written public comment period of at least 90 days. The Secretary shall consider such comments and include a summary thereof in the management plan.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Plan submission","label":"e Plan submission","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s13523","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs13523%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Within one year after , the Secretary shall submit the first management plan under this section to Congress. Thereafter, the Secretary shall submit a revised management plan biennially, at the time of submittal of the President’s annual budget submission to the Congress.October 24, 1992","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
